1
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:31,010
Captain Sun.

2
00:01:31,240 --> 00:01:31,970
Brother Yan.

3
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:33,570
Captain Sun,

4
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:35,130
we brought Wu Xiaoyan back.

5
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:37,680
Why did you bring her back?

6
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:38,360
We found out

7
00:01:38,360 --> 00:01:39,640
that Wu Xiaoyan is a local.

8
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:40,840
Right after coming of age,

9
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:41,880
she went to work.

10
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:43,520
But just half a month ago,

11
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:44,600
she suddenly quit her job.

12
00:01:44,600 --> 00:01:46,080
Even her dad couldn't contact her.

13
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:47,560
She said she was going out of town for work,

14
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,520
but she didn't leave.

15
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:50,050
She stayed in a small motel.

16
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:51,820
When we found her at the motel,

17
00:01:52,479 --> 00:01:53,280
we found this.

18
00:01:55,479 --> 00:01:56,440
So we thought

19
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:58,960
it'd be safer to bring her back for questioning.

20
00:01:58,960 --> 00:02:00,220
Kong Jiao's bankbook.

21
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:00,920
Right.

22
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:03,600
Did you check Ma Jinguang's alibi?

23
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:04,920
He said on the night of the 14th,

24
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:05,880
at the time of the crime,

25
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:07,340
he was working in the mine.

26
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,300
We are still verifying it.

27
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:13,720
Hey.

28
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:14,640
Lao Yan,

29
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:15,800
Lao Yan,

30
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,000
where are you going?

31
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:17,660
To the mine.

32
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:19,570
Captain Sun.

33
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:21,170
Captain Sun.

34
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:24,290
Wu Xiaoyan is still inside.

35
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:25,480
Oh.

36
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:57,050
Did something happen to Jiaojiao?

37
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:58,520
How did you know

38
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:00,380
something happened to Kong Jiao?

39
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:03,560
Did Ma Jinguang hit her again?

40
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,840
Is she badly hurt?

41
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:05,960
Which hospital is Jiaojiao in now?

42
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:06,880
How is she?

43
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:07,840
Calm down first.

44
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:09,520
Listen to Captain Sun explain the situation.

45
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,050
Sit down.

46
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:12,920
Don't worry.

47
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:15,240
We just want to get some basic information.

48
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:15,960
You can start by telling us

49
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,890
your relationship with Kong Jiao.

50
00:03:18,079 --> 00:03:18,640
Friends.

51
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:19,680
Good friends.

52
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:21,200
Like real sisters.

53
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,620
What are you doing?

54
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:23,240
Hey.

55
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:25,720
If you keep doing this, I'll call the police.

56
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:26,600
What are you doing?

57
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:27,760
In front of everyone.

58
00:03:27,760 --> 00:03:29,620
Harassing the lady boss, are you?

59
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:31,160
My brother is a cop.

60
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:32,520
Want me to call him now?

61
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:33,560
Just you wait.

62
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:35,480
A real man doesn't fight a woman.

63
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,120
Thank you.

64
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,560
Actually, I was lying to him.

65
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:45,680
I don't have a cop brother at all.

66
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,160
But,

67
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,690
that thing you have,

68
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:51,000
I have one too.

69
00:03:52,079 --> 00:03:54,079
We all yearn for a free life.

70
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:55,760
What family brings us

71
00:03:55,920 --> 00:03:57,780
is nothing but violence and harm.

72
00:03:58,160 --> 00:03:59,640
Under the guise of love, Ma Jinguang

73
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:01,500
controlled and abused Jiaojiao.

74
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:09,880
Why was Kong Jiao's passbook

75
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:11,120
found in your house?

76
00:04:14,720 --> 00:04:16,180
Because we wanted to leave

77
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:17,880
and live a free life.

78
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,079
To leave,

79
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:21,079
we definitely needed money.

80
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:21,920
Come.

81
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:23,680
Take it.

82
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:27,120
Ma Jinguang looks at me like a thief.

83
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:28,320
Hide it well.

84
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,640
When we save enough money,

85
00:04:29,640 --> 00:04:30,360
we will leave.

86
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,840
But if he finds out the bankbook is gone,

87
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:32,960
he will kill you.

88
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:36,040
Every cent here is mine.

89
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:38,080
It has absolutely nothing to do with Ma Jinguang.

90
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:39,210
I've made up my mind.

91
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:41,560
I have to live for myself from now on.

92
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:42,720
Every month,

93
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:45,320
we secretly deposited some money into this bankbook.

94
00:04:45,320 --> 00:04:47,159
We've been saving for over two years.

95
00:04:47,159 --> 00:04:48,820
At the beginning of the month,

96
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:50,320
Jiaojiao said she'd stop saving.

97
00:04:50,320 --> 00:04:52,880
She couldn't stand Ma Jinguang anymore.

98
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,880
We had to leave immediately.

99
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:56,360
So we agreed,

100
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,340
on the seventh,

101
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:59,090
we would set off on the seventh.

102
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:00,800
I quit my job in advance

103
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,160
and snuck out of the house.

104
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,960
I secretly moved into a small hotel.

105
00:05:03,960 --> 00:05:05,640
I waited here for her to call me,

106
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:07,800
but in the end, I couldn't reach her.

107
00:05:07,880 --> 00:05:10,080
When was the last time you saw Kong Jiao?

108
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,520
Early... early this month,

109
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:13,520
around the third.

110
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:15,280
Have you been in the hotel the whole time?

111
00:05:15,280 --> 00:05:16,680
Did you go anywhere else?

112
00:05:17,080 --> 00:05:19,000
I've been in the hotel the whole time.

113
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:21,460
Because Jiaojiao told me not to look for her.

114
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:24,160
She said she had to deal with Ma Jinguang first.

115
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,280
But when it was time to leave,

116
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,440
she didn't show up.

117
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:29,040
I couldn't reach her either,

118
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,760
so I got a little scared.

119
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:31,840
Did you know?

120
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,360
Before, Ma Jinguang

121
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:35,159
would secretly check her phone.

122
00:05:35,159 --> 00:05:36,560
Once, when he was following Jiaojiao,

123
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,560
he bumped into us.

124
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:38,920
He even said

125
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:41,000
if I misled Jiaojiao again,

126
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,960
he would chop my head off.

127
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:44,120
Officer,

128
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,800
can you please tell me first,

129
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:47,330
what happened to Jiaojiao?

130
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:55,440
Is there anyone who can prove

131
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:57,240
that you've been in the hotel the whole time?

132
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,000
Prove?

133
00:05:59,080 --> 00:05:59,760
Why do I need to

134
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:00,480
prove it?

135
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:03,610
We'll confirm it later.

136
00:06:08,760 --> 00:06:09,640
You can go back.

137
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:11,320
If there's any information we can disclose,

138
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:12,920
we will contact you anytime.

139
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:14,760
Officer!

140
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:17,240
Jiaojiao is badly hurt this time, isn't she?

141
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,640
It must be Ma Jinguang.

142
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:19,880
Did you arrest him?

143
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:20,600
Kong Jiao

144
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:22,080
was murdered.

145
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:25,600
But believe us,

146
00:06:26,640 --> 00:06:28,700
we will definitely catch the killer.

147
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,360
Hey.

148
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,860
What are you doing?

149
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,480
Having a meal.

150
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:50,570
Brother,

151
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:53,320
is the mine still short of hands?

152
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:54,840
I don't know

153
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:56,080
if we are short of hands.

154
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:57,409
You have to ask the boss.

155
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:58,280
Hey,

156
00:06:58,640 --> 00:07:00,170
how did you find this place?

157
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:03,280
Ma Jinguang recommended me.

158
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:04,200
Ma Jinguang?

159
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:06,980
Who is Ma Jinguang?

160
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:07,680
Oh.

161
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:09,400
You mean Ma Gangdan'er.

162
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:10,040
Yeah.

163
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:10,960
Brother,

164
00:07:11,520 --> 00:07:13,320
is it tiring working in this mine?

165
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:14,880
How often do you get a break?

166
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:17,040
Twelve-hour shifts.

167
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:19,180
The bell rings every three hours,

168
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,700
and we rest for 15 minutes.

169
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:22,360
Saying it's not tiring

170
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,320
is a lie.

171
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:23,920
Hey.

172
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:26,280
But the boss pays alright.

173
00:07:26,640 --> 00:07:27,700
If you want to come,

174
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:29,040
I'll talk to the boss.

175
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:32,960
Is the bell accurate?

176
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:35,360
My previous boss was very greedy.

177
00:07:35,640 --> 00:07:36,400
He promised

178
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:38,040
the bell would ring every two hours,

179
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:38,640
but actually,

180
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:40,900
it might not ring even after three hours.

181
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:42,360
Every time it rang,

182
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,640
the break was over before

183
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:44,760
I could finish a cigarette.

184
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:46,000
Not here.

185
00:07:46,280 --> 00:07:47,040
The bell

186
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:48,840
is managed by Ma Gangdan'er.

187
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:50,400
He's smart.

188
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:52,480
He got some electronic bell.

189
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:55,440
Electronic bell?

190
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:57,700
An electronic bell can be rigged too.

191
00:07:58,280 --> 00:07:59,610
On the night of the 14th,

192
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,680
when I was drinking with Ma Jinguang,

193
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:03,240
he bragged that

194
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:05,040
he could make the bell as long

195
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:06,370
or as short as he wanted.

196
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,340
Son of a bitch, Ma Gangdan'er.

197
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:11,380
No wonder when he left on the 14th,

198
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:13,480
I felt something was wrong.

199
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:15,760
Really?

200
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:18,160
Did he want to

201
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,760
sneak out to drink

202
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:21,640
and trick you into working more?

203
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:23,800
Probably.

204
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:26,780
What are you doing?

205
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:28,880
He's looking for work.

206
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:30,640
I was just going to tell the boss.

207
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:31,760
Ah, right.

208
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,080
Looking for work.

209
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,490
With your fair skin,

210
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:36,280
you don't look like a laborer.

211
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:37,280
What exactly are you doing here?

212
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:38,409
What are you asking?

213
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,280
Damn it.

214
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,000
You little brat,

215
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,240
are probably here to inspect the mine.

216
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,500
Smashing my rice bowl!

217
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:45,760
Beat him!

218
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:52,920
Police!

219
00:08:57,640 --> 00:08:58,320
Old Yan.

220
00:09:03,040 --> 00:09:04,160
What's the situation?

221
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:05,040
Assaulting a police officer.

222
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:05,640
Hey, hey, hey!

223
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:06,560
No, no, no!

224
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,320
No, officer.

225
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:07,680
I...

226
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:10,050
We didn't know he was a police officer.

227
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:11,840
So if he's not a police officer, you can just beat him up?

228
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:12,240
Ah.

229
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:13,640
We just wanted to scare him.

230
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:15,440
We didn't really want to hit him.

231
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,880
You are all so tough.

232
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:26,360
How dare you assault police?

233
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:26,890
Jia Peng,

234
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:27,860
take them back.

235
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:28,840
Take all of them back.

236
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,560
Forget it.

237
00:09:30,280 --> 00:09:31,280
They just want

238
00:09:31,280 --> 00:09:32,360
to keep their jobs.

239
00:09:32,800 --> 00:09:33,400
Jia Peng,

240
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:36,460
inform the brother department to investigate.

241
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,440
I ask you again.

242
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:41,130
On the night of the 14th,

243
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,520
when Ma Jinguang went out,

244
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:44,320
how many times did the bell ring?

245
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,400
Did you notice

246
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:47,400
that the bell rang at the wrong time?

247
00:09:47,560 --> 00:09:48,480
On the 14th,

248
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,400
when Ma Jinguang left,

249
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:52,600
the work bell rang once.

250
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:54,970
The break bell rang.

251
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:56,400
As soon as he came back,

252
00:09:56,400 --> 00:09:57,960
the work bell rang again.

253
00:09:58,600 --> 00:09:59,640
But I felt

254
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:02,370
this time the work bell rang for a bit too long.

255
00:10:02,920 --> 00:10:05,480
I thought the boss told Ma Jinguang to do it,

256
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:06,440
so

257
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:08,120
I didn't dare to say anything.

258
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:09,440
No wonder we worked for so long that day.

259
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,240
It was so long.

260
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:12,400
I almost pooped my pants.

261
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:14,300
Any other unusual things?

262
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:15,370
I don't know.

263
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:16,560
Ma Gangdan asked me for a rope.

264
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:17,760
Does that count?

265
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:19,120
How is that

266
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:20,560
an unusual thing?

267
00:10:20,640 --> 00:10:22,520
He returned it to you right away.

268
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:25,680
He borrowed it when he left

269
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:26,800
and returned it when he came back.

270
00:10:26,800 --> 00:10:28,040
That was too fast.

271
00:10:28,280 --> 00:10:29,280
Where is the rope?

272
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:33,960
Ma Jinguang said he left the mine after 8:00

273
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,960
and came back before the second break,

274
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:38,280
which was 12:00.

275
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:40,000
So he didn't have time to commit the crime.

276
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:42,360
But what if he changed the bell interval

277
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:43,840
from two hours

278
00:10:44,520 --> 00:10:46,000
to two and a half hours,

279
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:47,640
or even three hours?

280
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,640
Then the time he returned to the mine

281
00:10:49,640 --> 00:10:51,080
would be 1:00 a.m.

282
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,360
or even 2:00 a.m.,

283
00:10:52,760 --> 00:10:54,680
meaning he had plenty of time to commit the crime.

284
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:55,760
He previously admitted

285
00:10:55,760 --> 00:10:58,640
he had a problem with Zhang Biao and Kong Jiao's contact.

286
00:10:58,640 --> 00:10:59,480
Coupled with

287
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:01,320
what Wu Xiaoyan said,

288
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:03,000
I think

289
00:11:03,400 --> 00:11:05,600
there is reason to suspect Ma Jinguang.

290
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,840
He does have a motive,

291
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:10,240
and he lied about his alibi.

292
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:12,320
But we still lack

293
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:14,520
direct evidence of his involvement in the crime.

294
00:11:14,520 --> 00:11:15,360
But the fact that he lied

295
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:16,960
already makes him a suspect.

296
00:11:17,880 --> 00:11:19,520
Now it depends on whether the rope

297
00:11:19,520 --> 00:11:21,650
contains any traces of the crime scene

298
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:23,040
and the body.

299
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:50,000
Hello?

300
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:51,400
Where are you?

301
00:11:51,640 --> 00:11:52,440
Where are you?

302
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:54,400
None of your business where I am.

303
00:11:54,400 --> 00:11:55,460
Did you come alone?

304
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:56,840
Of course.

305
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:58,360
Otherwise, why would I have brought a few more people

306
00:11:58,360 --> 00:11:59,620
to play cards with you?

307
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:01,600
Did you bring the money?

308
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:02,000
Yes.

309
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:04,440
Where are you?

310
00:12:04,680 --> 00:12:06,720
Why is a grown man dawdling like this?

311
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:07,480
Don't forget

312
00:12:07,800 --> 00:12:09,160
what I did for you.

313
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:12,530
What do you want?

314
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,280
Cut the crap.

315
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:15,780
Keep driving forward.

316
00:12:29,560 --> 00:12:30,520
Ma Jinguang!

317
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:32,640
You beast! Hey!

318
00:12:32,640 --> 00:12:33,280
Hey!

319
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:33,880
What are you doing?

320
00:12:33,880 --> 00:12:35,560
Why did you kill Jiaojiao?

321
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:36,880
You killed my wife.

322
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:38,240
Ma Jinguang!

323
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,840
Do you know what I did for her?

324
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,080
It was you.

325
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:43,200
Why did you treat Jiaojiao like this?

326
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,080
Ma Jinguang!

327
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,800
Can getting physical solve the problem?

328
00:12:45,800 --> 00:12:47,660
Is this how you treated Kong Jiao?

329
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:48,920
If you can't win the argument, you use your fists.

330
00:12:48,920 --> 00:12:50,400
If she disobeys, you beat her.

331
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:53,600
You admit to domestic violence against Kong Jiao, right?

332
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:56,400
What if she doesn't learn her lesson?

333
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:58,000
Then beat her until she does.

334
00:12:58,120 --> 00:12:59,320
Did you all hear that?

335
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:00,520
It was him.

336
00:13:00,760 --> 00:13:02,000
He must have killed Jiaojiao.

337
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:02,800
Ma Jinguang!

338
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:04,400
Let me tell you.

339
00:13:05,160 --> 00:13:06,820
Nothing you say now will help.

340
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:11,170
Confess everything you did first.

341
00:13:11,280 --> 00:13:12,080
Take him away.

342
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:12,640
Move.

343
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:14,320
Move.

344
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:24,680
Yan.

345
00:13:26,520 --> 00:13:28,040
Don't pin this on me.

346
00:13:29,280 --> 00:13:30,480
I didn't do anything.

347
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:32,460
You just want to ruin me

348
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:36,380
and close the case to take the credit, don't you?

349
00:13:37,520 --> 00:13:40,120
Ma Jinguang, if you're going to talk like that,

350
00:13:40,400 --> 00:13:42,330
we really have nothing to discuss.

351
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:49,800
I did go home that day,

352
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:53,330
but I wouldn't kill my own wife.

353
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:56,960
I wanted her to stay.

354
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:00,840
Kong Jiao.

355
00:14:02,520 --> 00:14:03,400
That night,

356
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:05,640
I arrived at Jiaojiao's place past eight.

357
00:14:05,640 --> 00:14:08,880
But no matter how hard I knocked, she wouldn't open the door.

358
00:14:08,880 --> 00:14:10,280
I called her, but there was no sound inside.

359
00:14:10,280 --> 00:14:11,210
I was very angry.

360
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:14,300
I admit I went to her place with a purpose.

361
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:16,840
She insisted on leaving.

362
00:14:17,800 --> 00:14:18,440
I thought,

363
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:21,580
if that didn't work, I'd tie her up first,

364
00:14:21,600 --> 00:14:22,280
talk to her nicely,

365
00:14:22,280 --> 00:14:24,010
and make her come to her senses.

366
00:14:24,400 --> 00:14:25,640
But there was no one home when I got there,

367
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:27,700
and I couldn't reach her on the phone.

368
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:29,980
After waiting for a long time,

369
00:14:30,120 --> 00:14:31,160
I took the stairs

370
00:14:31,280 --> 00:14:32,040
and left.

371
00:14:36,280 --> 00:14:38,000
When I got downstairs, I figured it out.

372
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:40,000
She was just momentarily obsessed.

373
00:14:40,240 --> 00:14:41,360
Once she's out there,

374
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:43,020
she'll know after she suffers

375
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:45,000
who loves her the most in this world,

376
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:46,200
and she'll come back.

377
00:14:49,440 --> 00:14:50,200
Who knew...

378
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:57,280
You went home with a rope,

379
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:59,460
and left without doing anything?

380
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:00,720
If you didn't do anything,

381
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:01,640
why did you lie?

382
00:15:02,120 --> 00:15:03,720
You planned this for so long,

383
00:15:03,760 --> 00:15:06,420
even adjusting the electronic bell in the mine.

384
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:08,240
And now you're telling me

385
00:15:08,240 --> 00:15:10,480
you suddenly changed your mind and left?

386
00:15:10,480 --> 00:15:12,140
Ma Jinguang, I'm warning you.

387
00:15:12,640 --> 00:15:14,160
This is your last chance.

388
00:15:14,920 --> 00:15:15,980
I adjusted the bell

389
00:15:16,560 --> 00:15:18,280
to get fined less.

390
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:20,800
Thirty yuan an hour

391
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:24,730
is my family's grocery money for a day.

392
00:15:32,720 --> 00:15:34,580
You don't believe anything I say.

393
00:15:38,600 --> 00:15:39,330
Ma Jinguang.

394
00:15:39,880 --> 00:15:41,800
Do you know what we just

395
00:15:41,840 --> 00:15:43,160
detected on you?

396
00:15:45,000 --> 00:15:47,800
As long as you've been in contact with explosives,

397
00:15:48,320 --> 00:15:49,840
the device can detect it.

398
00:15:51,160 --> 00:15:52,620
With current technology,

399
00:15:53,080 --> 00:15:55,540
the sensitivity can reach nanogram levels.

400
00:15:56,040 --> 00:15:57,500
The results just came out.

401
00:16:00,320 --> 00:16:01,200
Positive.

402
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:04,320
Tell us the truth.

403
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:06,360
Did you use,

404
00:16:06,560 --> 00:16:07,240
transport,

405
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:08,490
or make explosives?

406
00:16:09,400 --> 00:16:10,480
I am a miner.

407
00:16:11,280 --> 00:16:13,080
Mining requires blasting.

408
00:16:13,760 --> 00:16:15,440
Go check with that piece of paper of yours.

409
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:17,320
Where in the mine doesn't have

410
00:16:17,760 --> 00:16:19,890
the explosive residue you mentioned?

411
00:16:20,560 --> 00:16:21,890
You just want to ruin me.

412
00:16:22,480 --> 00:16:23,360
Ma Jinguang, I'm telling you,

413
00:16:23,360 --> 00:16:25,480
we will absolutely enforce the law impartially.

414
00:16:25,480 --> 00:16:27,880
But the premise is you need to tell the truth

415
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:29,600
for us to believe you.

416
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:30,840
You won't believe me.

417
00:16:30,920 --> 00:16:32,440
You don't believe anything.

418
00:16:32,440 --> 00:16:35,570
You just think a criminal's son will also commit crimes.

419
00:16:35,680 --> 00:16:37,210
What you want to hear most is

420
00:16:37,520 --> 00:16:40,320
that Ma Guangfu is a murderer who bombed a cop,

421
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:43,440
and Ma Jinguang is a murderer who killed his wife.

422
00:17:08,960 --> 00:17:10,319
Mr. Wang's report is out.

423
00:17:10,319 --> 00:17:11,240
On that rope,

424
00:17:11,599 --> 00:17:13,839
Kong Jiao's DNA was indeed not detected.

425
00:17:13,839 --> 00:17:15,680
Not even a microscopic trace of skin flakes

426
00:17:15,680 --> 00:17:16,319
was found.

427
00:17:16,319 --> 00:17:17,240
Which means

428
00:17:17,560 --> 00:17:19,890
Kong Jiao really never touched that rope.

429
00:17:21,520 --> 00:17:23,520
Judging from his reaction just now,

430
00:17:24,119 --> 00:17:25,780
I do have some suspicions too.

431
00:17:26,319 --> 00:17:28,450
But why would he hide this experience?

432
00:17:29,120 --> 00:17:30,450
Where exactly did he go?

433
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:36,480
Three cases

434
00:17:37,680 --> 00:17:39,740
with completely different methods.

435
00:17:40,320 --> 00:17:42,250
Every one was carefully designed,

436
00:17:42,960 --> 00:17:45,890
almost entirely wiping out all traces of the crimes,

437
00:17:47,480 --> 00:17:48,360
yet

438
00:17:50,200 --> 00:17:52,530
full of provocations against the police.

439
00:17:53,320 --> 00:17:55,920
There is a faint connection between the victims,

440
00:17:55,920 --> 00:17:57,980
which seems to be hiding some secret.

441
00:17:58,880 --> 00:18:00,240
What kind of person

442
00:18:01,080 --> 00:18:02,440
is doing such things?

443
00:18:03,840 --> 00:18:04,440
And why

444
00:18:07,840 --> 00:18:09,000
is he doing it?

445
00:18:13,080 --> 00:18:15,200
We can't release Ma Jinguang yet.

446
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:17,860
He is definitely suspicious.

447
00:18:24,920 --> 00:18:26,380
We found the tattooed man.

448
00:18:31,400 --> 00:18:33,330
Collecting money is such a hassle.

449
00:18:35,520 --> 00:18:36,520
I told you to do it quietly.

450
00:18:36,520 --> 00:18:37,680
Who told you to make so much noise?

451
00:18:37,680 --> 00:18:39,320
This is blood money.

452
00:18:39,400 --> 00:18:40,640
If you aren't afraid, I am.

